8798599e-fb34-4fd0-908c-9740b0dbbf34.4a2f1e83-f596-47fb-a679-82c3244c168d.description=This workflow returns the component properties and values using Artifact APIs.

result\:
propertyNameValuesList\: pipe separated list of property name and values ( where each property name and values would be ; seprated and multiple values would be , seprated)
e.g. - property 1; value1,value2|property 2; value3|property 3; value3,value4|........ 8798599e-fb34-4fd0-908c-9740b0dbbf34.da10759c-b2d7-49d6-8299-48b4e48a2df8.description=Populates a CI in ESL.

Inputs\:

hostName - Name of the CI/Server (not FQDN). Adds the domain from the system properties
parentName - Name of the parent CI (no FQDN). example\: farm name for the VM
osType - Type of OS. Acceptable values\: Windows, Linux
osVersion - Version of OS as in ESL (case-sensitive). example\: Windows 2008 Enterprise R2, Windows 2008 Standard R2, Windows 2012 Standard R2, LINUX RedHat EL 6.6 64bit, LINUX SuSE Enterprise Server 11 64bit
serverEnvironment - Production / Development
serverFunction - Business Application, Database, Middleware
systemContact - Technical owner mail id
ipAddress - Primary IP address of the CI 8798599e-fb34-4fd0-908c-9740b0dbbf34.e5285806-8dcd-462d-a882-03b98d93609f.prompt=User Identifier
flow.name: Test ESL Manual Flow
